I was programmed to protect Sarah Connor.

366
00:31:54,560 --> 00:31:56,100
我會一直保護她
I will not stop.

367
00:31:56,700 --> 00:31:58,907
是誰給你設定的  啊  誰送他回來的
Yeah? Programmed by who? Huh? Who sent him back?

368
00:31:59,020 --> 00:32:00,624
