Those files have been erased.

369
00:32:00,740 --> 00:32:01,821
噢  好借口啊
Oh, that's convenient.

370
00:32:01,940 --> 00:32:03,544
那人不想讓我們知道他
Whoever sent him, they don't want us to know.

371
00:32:03,660 --> 00:32:05,469
不管是我  是他  還是其他人
Not me, not him, not anyone.

372
00:32:05,620 --> 00:32:07,622
這樣天網就沒法設定救我的那個人了
So Skynet can't target the person who saved me.

373
00:32:07,740 --> 00:32:10,664
從邏輯上看  有人想讓莎拉·康納活下去
Logically, it is someone who wants Sarah Connor to live.

374
00:32:11,900 --> 00:32:13,400
