All of it. This is not the mission.

382
00:33:08,420 --> 00:33:11,230
我想跟你說的是  瑞斯
That's what I'm trying to tell you, Reese.

383
00:33:11,340 --> 00:33:14,867
那個你回來要保護的女孩兒  已經不在了
The girl that you came back for, she's gone.

384
00:33:16,300 --> 00:33:18,223
我不需要別人保護
I don't need saving.

385
00:33:18,980 --> 00:33:20,266
現在有新任務
There's a new mission.

386
00:33:20,340 --> 00:33:21,546
什麼任務
Oh, yeah? Which is?

387
00:33:23,140 --> 00:33:26,542
如果過去可以改變  那麼未來也一樣
If the past can change, then so can the future.

388
00:33:26,900 --> 00:33:31,030
我們完全可以阻止宣判日的到來  永遠
We can stop Judgment Day from happening. Ever.

389
00:33:32,980 --> 00:33:35,347
在天網誕生前消滅它
Kill Skynet before it's born.

390
00:33:35,980 --> 00:33:37,266
什麼
What?

391
00:33:41,620 --> 00:33:42,746
趴下
Get down!

392
00:33:42,820 --> 00:33:43,946
我們被發現了
We have been reacquired.

393
00:33:44,020 --> 00:33:45,226
怎麼可能  見鬼
Uh, yeah. No shit!

394
00:34:11,220 --> 00:34:12,460
