你說過去的變化改變了你
You said it happened 'cause the past was altered.

400
00:35:20,540 --> 00:35:21,541
怎麼回事兒
How?

401
00:35:21,620 --> 00:35:22,860
這很重要嗎
Oh, does that matter?

402
00:35:23,260 --> 00:35:24,705
跟我說說  莎拉
How, Sarah?

403
00:35:26,020 --> 00:35:29,183
有個終結者回到了我小的時候
A terminator was sent after me when I was a kid, okay?

404
00:35:30,020 --> 00:35:32,864
終結者只來自一個地方  未來
Terminators only come from one place, the future.

405
00:35:39,420 --> 00:35:40,945
但未來改變了
Something happened.

406
00:35:41,220 --> 00:35:42,506
是啊  所以呢
Okay. So?

407
00:35:42,900 --> 00:35:44,500
- 我可能看到了  - 什麼
- I think I might have seen it. - What...

408
00:35:44,900 --> 00:35:46,504
你這話什麼意思
What are you talking about?

409
