幫我一下
You got to help me.

421
00:39:26,100 --> 00:39:27,226
我受傷了
I'm hurt.

422
00:39:27,660 --> 00:39:28,707
莎拉
Sarah?

423
00:39:31,420 --> 00:39:32,751
見鬼
Shit.

424
00:39:37,020 --> 00:39:38,909
嘿  是我  莎拉
Hey, it's me, Sarah!

425
00:39:39,260 --> 00:39:40,625
莎拉  他在說謊
Sarah, he's lying.

426
00:39:41,180 --> 00:39:42,181
嘿
Hey.

427
00:39:42,780 --> 00:39:44,191
他是假的  我才是瑞斯
He's the machine. I'm Reese.

428
00:39:44,340 --> 00:39:45,626
莎拉
It's me, Sarah.

429
00:39:46,660 --> 00:39:48,628
你聽我說  終結者沒死  它襲擊了我
All right, listen, the terminator's not dead. It attacked me!

430
00:39:48,740 --> 00:39:50,230
他能模仿我
Sarah, you said they could mimic.

431
00:39:50,380 --> 00:39:51,427
是我  莎拉
It's me, Sarah!

432
00:39:51,500 --> 00:39:54,470
- 他是假的  開槍  - 我才是瑞斯  衝他開槍
- He's mimicking. Shoot him! - I'm Reese! Shoot him!

433
00:40:02,140 --> 00:40:03,744
這招不錯
Nice try.

434
00:40:04,100 --> 00:40:05,101
快跑
Run!

435
00:41:06,100 --> 00:41:07,943
你怎麼知道他是終結者
How'd you know which one was him?

436
00:41:08,300 --> 00:41:10,667
這個  其實我不知道
Well, I didn't know exactly.

437
00:41:11,020 --> 00:41:12,545
萬一你打到我呢
You could have shot me!

438
00:41:12,860 --> 00:41:15,340
可是至少我確定不是你
Well, I was pretty sure it wasn't you.

439
00:41:16,700 --> 00:41:17,986
你真確定
Pretty sure?

440
00:41:18,380 --> 00:41:20,951
我們早已經為你的到來做好準備了
We've been prepping for you to arrive for over a decade.

441
00:41:21,060 --> 00:41:22,346
還有它
That, too.

442
00:41:23,140 --> 00:41:25,347
- 所以這是個陷阱  - 當然了
- So you set a trap. - Had to.

443
00:41:25,940 --> 00:41:28,227
我們去之前還真用得上它
Can't leave any future tech behind when we go.

444
00:41:28,540 --> 00:41:29,666
什麼
Go?

445
00:41:30,380 --> 00:41:31,666
去哪兒
Go where?

446
00:41:34,220 --> 00:41:35,870
噢  這不是
That's...

447
00:41:36,180 --> 00:41:37,864
一台時空轉換機
A Time Displacement Device.

448
00:41:37,980 --> 00:41:40,187
是啊  怎麼看著像是一堆破爛兒
Yeah, well, it looks like a piece of junk.

449
00:41:40,300 --> 00:41:42,020
這個時代擁有的科技
There's no governing technology in this time

450
00:41:42,100 --> 00:41:44,262
沒有辦法操控這台機器
that can control the displacement circuits.

451
00:41:44,380 --> 00:41:47,543
你得用未來的中央處理器才能操控它
You needed the CPU from the future to make it run.

452
00:41:48,380 --> 00:41:50,144
而且顯然你不能用自己的
And you couldn't exactly use your own.

453
00:41:52,300 --> 00:41:54,380
我們只有一次機會  芯片會燒燬
We get one trip only. It's gonna fry the chip,

454
00:41:54,460 --> 00:41:56,508
而且整個洛杉磯的電力會耗光
and take out most of the L.A. city power grid.

455
00:41:57,300 --> 00:41:58,381
好了嗎
Are we ready?

456
00:41:58,500 --> 00:42:00,502
坐標已經設定為1997年
The coordinates are set for 1997.

457
00:42:00,780 --> 00:42:02,589
你要快點兒登上傳輸台
You must leave as soon as possible.

458
00:42:02,900 --> 00:42:05,870
我們  是你和我  一起去
We. We're going. All of us.

459
00:42:07,740 --> 00:42:09,708
我表皮的恢復需要很多年
My flesh will take years to regrow.

460
00:42:10,020 --> 00:42:11,226
我不能跟你去
I cannot come with you

461
00:42:11,380 --> 00:42:13,020
我得考慮到量子場的磁場效應
due to the magnetics of the quantum field.

462
00:42:13,060 --> 00:42:14,061
老爹
Pops!

463
00:42:14,140 --> 00:42:16,029
你想讓我們穿越時間
You want us to time travel?

464
00:42:16,140 --> 00:42:19,030
去未來  用這玩意兒
Into the future. In that?

465
00:42:19,140 --> 00:42:20,426
對  我們還不能穿衣服
Yeah, we can't be wearing anything.

466
00:42:20,540 --> 00:42:22,110
我知道穿越時間有什麼要求
Yeah, I know how time travel works.

467
00:42:22,260 --> 00:42:24,260
- 莎拉  - 你別想阻止我幹這件事
- Sarah... - Look, don't try and talk me out of it.

468
00:42:24,340 --> 00:42:27,230
我知道你怎麼想的  把我關在一間屋子裏
Look, I know you think you're here so you can just lock me in a room

469
00:42:27,340 --> 00:42:28,705
然後等我生下那個反叛軍首領
until I give birth to the leader of the Resistance.

470
