是2017年
2017.

476
00:42:41,380 --> 00:42:43,348
應該是2017年10月
Yeah, October 2017.

477
00:42:43,460 --> 00:42:45,986
不  太晚了  那已經是宣判日之後了
No, that's too late. That's after Judgment Day.

478
00:42:46,140 --> 00:42:47,266
你不是說一切都變了嗎
No, you said everything's changed,

479
00:42:47,340 --> 00:42:48,387
這你也是對的
and you're right about that, too.

480
00:42:48,540 --> 00:42:49,621
莎拉
Sarah...

481
00:42:52,780 --> 00:42:55,863
我看到了另一個沒有發生戰爭的未來
Look, I've seen a world where the bombs never fell.

482
00:42:56,300 --> 00:42:58,109
一樣的房子
All right? The same house.

483
00:42:58,540 --> 00:43:00,144
一樣的家人
The same parents.

484
00:43:01,820 --> 00:43:04,107
一樣的我  不一樣的是
It was the same me, only I was...

485
00:43:06,300 --> 00:43:07,665
我在家裏
I was home.

486
00:43:08,140 --> 00:43:10,188
那是我13歲的生日
It was my 13th birthday.

487
00:43:10,300 --> 00:43:13,986
在夢中看到你的家人還在  這什麼也說明不了
A dream of having your family back doesn't mean a thing.

488
00:43:15,140 --> 00:43:16,141
相信我
Trust me.

489
00:43:16,500 --> 00:43:18,502
這不是夢  這  這是段記憶
Not a dream, all right? A memory.

490
00:43:19,140 --> 00:43:21,029
我現在只能記住一些片段
I can't hold on to all of it, just moments,

491
00:43:21,100 --> 00:43:23,148
我收到了一條信息
but I was given a message.

492
00:43:25,500 --> 00:43:27,628
你能在天網誕生前消滅它
"You can kill Skynet before it's born."

493
00:43:28,820 --> 00:43:31,300
天網就是創世紀
"Skynet is Genisys."

494
00:43:31,820 --> 00:43:34,141
天網在2017年10月正式上線
It comes online October 2017.

495
00:43:34,500 --> 00:43:36,901
它一旦上線  審判日就會到來
And when it does, Judgment Day happens.

496
00:43:37,020 --> 00:43:38,146
你是在回憶未來嗎
So you're remembering the future?

497
00:43:38,260 --> 00:43:39,307
不
No.

498
00:43:39,740 --> 00:43:42,311
那是另一條平行時間線上的你
The boy is the alternate timeline version of you.

499
00:43:42,980 --> 00:43:45,301
他是在回憶自己的過去
Kyle Reese is remembering his own past,

500
00:43:45,420 --> 00:43:46,990
也就是我們的未來
which is our future.

501
00:43:47,260 --> 00:43:48,989
你這解釋也太難懂了
That makes it so much better.

502
00:43:49,100 --> 00:43:50,943
他怎麼可能有兩條時間線的回憶
How can he be remembering two timelines?

503
