時間流中的某個連接點  就有可能
in the timeflow when you were in the quantum field.

505
00:43:56,540 --> 00:43:58,269
你  你能讓他說得通俗點兒嗎
Can you stop him talking like that?

506
00:43:58,380 --> 00:43:59,825
他身上有設置嗎
Is there a switch or something?

507
