給他的那一拳  把他腦子打壞了
his brain is scrambled from when you hit him on the head.

518
00:44:28,220 --> 00:44:29,346
莎拉
Sarah!

519
00:44:29,460 --> 00:44:33,590
我不知道  為什麼我會有一段不屬於我的回憶
I don't know why I'm remembering a life I never lived.

520
00:44:36,380 --> 00:44:37,870
