I can't let you do this.

525
00:44:59,020 --> 00:45:00,590
不管你怎麼想
I don't know you.

526
00:45:01,860 --> 00:45:04,101
要知道  這個  是我唯一能夠
But that is my one bullet

527
00:45:04,180 --> 00:45:06,786
徹底摧毀天網的武器
to fire at the heart of Skynet.

528
00:45:08,020 --> 00:45:10,944
你給我  把芯片  放回去
Give the chip back.

529
