Not without the risk of changing everything.

881
01:06:31,500 --> 01:06:33,150
你是我兒子
You're my son? You...

882
01:06:34,860 --> 01:06:36,305
我們的兒子
Our son?

883
01:06:36,420 --> 01:06:38,388
我很高興你終於知道了
I'm glad you finally know.

884
01:06:38,460 --> 01:06:40,349
我一直想找機會告訴你的
I have waited my whole life to tell you.

885
01:06:41,180 --> 01:06:42,989
