Why did you do that?

895
01:07:05,260 --> 01:07:06,671
因為他是屠殺機器
Because he's a killer!

896
01:07:10,860 --> 01:07:13,261
這才是你真正的程序
This was always your programming.

897
01:07:13,380 --> 01:07:14,905
找到約翰  並消滅他
Find John and terminate him.

898
01:07:18,420 --> 01:07:19,706
放開他
Let him go.

899
01:07:21,380 --> 01:07:22,825
