Right now!

900
01:07:57,300 --> 01:07:58,540
真疼啊
That hurt.

901
01:08:00,420 --> 01:08:02,661
不知道是真的疼  還是
Is that pain real, or was that

902
01:08:04,100 --> 01:08:08,105
