a trick of memory from when I was less?

903
01:08:09,620 --> 01:08:12,703
哇噢  這可有意思了
Well, this explains a lot.

904
01:08:13,550 --> 01:08:15,300
{\an8}掃瞄結果: 機械納米分子物質

905
01:08:15,350 --> 01:08:17,428
