Yeah. Who sent you back, I wonder?

906
01:08:17,700 --> 01:08:19,270
約翰  不
John, no.

907
01:08:20,380 --> 01:08:21,950
他不是約翰
It's not John.

908
01:08:24,700 --> 01:08:26,065
該死
Shit!

909
01:08:26,220 --> 01:08:28,302
