to safeguard Skynet's creation in this time.

931
01:09:37,380 --> 01:09:39,781
沒人能阻止審判日了
And in less than 24 hours,

932
01:09:40,580 --> 01:09:42,708
因為剩下已經不到24小時
no one will be able to stop Judgment Day.

933
01:09:43,420 --> 01:09:44,910
你到底想幹什麼
What do you want with us?

934
01:09:45,460 --> 01:09:50,022
我想提供一個新的  未來
I'm offering us a future.

935
