我們三個被困在這兒了
We're marooned, the three of us.

944
01:10:11,820 --> 01:10:13,743
我們被時間流放了
We're exiles in time.

945
01:10:15,300 --> 01:10:19,988
我可以殺了你  因為未來真的沒有希望了
You see, I can kill you, for there truly is no fate.

946
01:10:21,420 --> 01:10:22,546
加入我嗎
Are you with me?

947
01:10:23,300 --> 01:10:24,540
答案是不
The answer is no.

948
