957
01:11:42,380 --> 01:11:43,666
關掉它
Turn it off!

958
01:11:47,500 --> 01:11:48,661
快走
Come on!

959
01:11:48,820 --> 01:11:50,902
<i>全體醫護人員</i>
<i>Attention, all medical personnel.</i>

960
01:11:51,020 --> 01:11:53,626
<i>緊急疏散計劃已啟動</i>
<i>Evacuation procedures are now in progress.</i>

961
01:11:53,740 --> 01:11:54,787
調到最大
Crank it!

962
01:11:59,660 --> 01:12:00,661
老爹
Pops!

963
01:12:09,690 --> 01:12:10,854
我
I...

964
01:12:12,220 --> 01:12:16,270
以為你是個聰明人
thought you would be smarter,

965
01:12:21,020 --> 01:12:23,864
而且
and that...

966
01:12:24,900 --> 01:12:26,868
你會
you would...

967
01:12:28,060 --> 01:12:30,631
理解我
understand.

968
01:12:34,860 --> 01:12:36,464
對不起  約翰
I'm sorry, John.

969
01:12:45,380 --> 01:12:47,781
那機器拖不了他多久  快走
That thing won't hold him for long. Come on!

970
01:12:48,380 --> 01:12:49,506
瑞斯
Reese!

971
01:13:29,180 --> 01:13:31,911
不管天網對他做了什麼  我們就反著來
Whatever they did to him, we need to reverse it.

972
01:13:33,180 --> 01:13:34,306
得讓他變回原來的樣子
We need to get him back!

973
01:13:34,420 --> 01:13:37,390
他連人都稱不上  不知道他現在算什麼
He's not even human. We don't know what the hell he is.

974
01:13:37,500 --> 01:13:38,786
我知道
I do.

975
01:13:39,340 --> 01:13:41,468
在戰爭的末期  天網開始試圖
At the end of the war, Skynet was trying to develop

976
01:13:41,620 --> 01:13:43,588
製造一種新型的滲入單元
a new type of infiltration unit

977
01:13:43,700 --> 01:13:46,704
在人類實驗者體內植入分子機器人
by infecting human subjects with machine-phase matter.

978
01:13:46,860 --> 01:13:49,625
並且在細胞層面上對人體組織進行重組和再建
It restructures and rebuilds human tissue on a cellular level

979
01:13:49,780 --> 01:13:51,782
最大限度提升戰鬥力
for maximum combat utility.

980
01:13:53,540 --> 01:13:56,271
天網把約翰變成了一台終結者
Skynet's made John into a terminator.

981
01:13:57,500 --> 01:13:58,786
是的  凱爾·瑞斯
Yes, Kyle Reese.

982
01:13:59,220 --> 01:14:00,381
這樣機器就可以
They were trying to make a machine

983
01:14:00,460 --> 01:14:01,666
像人類一樣思考嗎
that could think like a man?

984
01:14:01,780 --> 01:14:03,464
但是實驗失敗了
But the experiments failed.

985
01:14:03,620 --> 01:14:06,464
實驗對像逐漸變得瘋狂  然後死掉
The human subjects went insane and died.

986
01:14:06,580 --> 01:14:09,026
是啊  約翰現在已經很瘋狂了
Yeah, well, John's got the crazy part down.

987
01:14:09,860 --> 01:14:12,022
那它有沒有什麼弱點
Does he have any weaknesses?

988
01:14:12,140 --> 01:14:14,302
分子機器人是利用磁場活動
Matter coheres using a magnetic field.

989
01:14:14,700 --> 01:14:16,987
