Disrupting that field may trap him.

990
01:14:17,260 --> 01:14:18,591
但是萬一能治好他呢
Right, but if he can be cured...

991
01:14:18,740 --> 01:14:21,949
不可能  他已經在細胞層面上改變了身體
Negative. His body was replaced on a cellular level.

992
01:14:22,060 --> 01:14:23,391
沒有治療方法
There is no cure.

993
01:14:23,500 --> 01:14:25,229
- 你怎麼什麼都知道  - 瑞斯
- You don't know that! - Reese...

994
01:14:25,340 --> 01:14:27,911
我才不會讓一台機器告訴我能做什麼
No, I'm not going to let a machine tell me what's possible!

995
01:14:28,020 --> 01:14:29,943
你說其他實驗對象都死了
You said all the other subjects died, right?

996
01:14:30,060 --> 01:14:32,060
那就說明他跟別人不一樣  他很獨特
Well, that means John's one-of-a-kind. He's unique!

997
01:14:32,100 --> 01:14:33,750
憑什麼說他不能被治癒
All right? There's no way of knowing what he's capable of.

998
01:14:33,820 --> 01:14:36,471
你說對了  這證明了他有多危險
You're right, and that's what makes him so dangerous!

999
01:14:37,500 --> 01:14:40,663
約翰現在已經不是人類最後的希望了
John is not humanity's last hope anymore.

1000
01:14:41,540 --> 01:14:43,383
他是天網的
He's Skynet's.

1001
