<i>It's a shame you won't take a more public role</i>

1003
01:14:48,460 --> 01:14:49,461
<i>真是太可惜了  約翰</i>
<i>in the company, John.</i>

1004
01:14:49,780 --> 01:14:51,145
丹尼已經是最棒的了
Danny is the best there is,

1005
01:14:51,260 --> 01:14:53,945
可連他也沒辦法破譯你在創世紀中
and even he can't decipher some of the enhanced code

1006
01:14:54,060 --> 01:14:55,300
設置的某些增強代碼
you've integrated into Genisys.

1007
01:14:55,340 --> 01:14:56,421
我知道這樣有效
I just know it works.

1008
01:14:56,540 --> 01:14:59,191
賽博丁要謝謝你  約翰
Cyberdyne owes you, John.

1009
01:15:00,220 --> 01:15:01,710
我也該謝你
I owe you.

1010
01:15:03,300 --> 01:15:05,180
