Miles, your faith in me is payment enough.

1011
01:15:05,220 --> 01:15:06,267
你組建了研發
You've funded the R&D.

1012
01:15:06,380 --> 01:15:09,031
還在過去的三年內大膽地採用了我的建議
You've taken the chances on my ideas for the last three years.

1013
01:15:09,140 --> 01:15:12,462
矩陣多邊擬態合金的應用潛力是不可估量的
The potential applications for polyalloy are countless.

1014
01:15:12,580 --> 01:15:15,948
你對機器人學有革命性貢獻
Your robotics work is revolutionary.

1015
01:15:16,060 --> 01:15:18,062
我果然沒看走眼
You were a good investment.

1016
01:15:18,140 --> 01:15:19,665
謝謝你的信任
I appreciate it.

1017
01:15:22,980 --> 01:15:23,981
