是啊
Yeah.

1027
01:15:49,620 --> 01:15:51,065
也是件好事
Good thing, too.

1028
01:15:52,020 --> 01:15:54,261
我們已經努力了好多年了
We're years away from making this thing work.

1029
01:15:54,780 --> 01:15:56,748
但是  當我們成功時
But when we do...

1030
