01:17:39,700 --> 01:17:41,862
小時候爸爸帶我來過這兒
My dad used to bring me here when I was little.

1054
01:17:41,980 --> 01:17:43,470
全都是房間  沒有人用
There are whole rooms that are abandoned.

1055
01:17:43,580 --> 01:17:45,184
所以我叫老爹好好利用它
That's why I told Pops to use it.

1056
01:17:45,300 --> 01:17:46,540
你們這兒有武器嗎
You got weapons down there?

1057
01:17:46,900 --> 01:17:50,188
武器  供給品  戰術裝備  服裝
Weapons, supplies, tactical gear, clothing.

1058
01:17:50,540 --> 01:17:53,020
還有褲子  凱爾·瑞斯
Including pants, Kyle Reese.

1059
01:17:53,140 --> 01:17:55,825
這是個玩笑  他會開玩笑
Was that a joke? Can he make jokes?

1060
01:18:06,500 --> 01:18:08,423
努力總算有回報了
I guess the long way pays off.

1061
01:18:09,260 --> 01:18:11,866
最後期限  30分鐘
We're on the clock. Thirty minutes.

1062
01:19:58,500 --> 01:19:59,547
老了
Old.

1063
01:20:01,220 --> 01:20:02,665
但還是能用
But not obsolete.

1064
01:20:03,340 --> 01:20:04,830
當然能用
Not yet.

1065
01:20:05,540 --> 01:20:06,826
我完事了
All done.

1066
01:20:09,580 --> 01:20:11,025
你們倆怎麼了
What's with you two?

1067
01:20:14,380 --> 01:20:15,984
服務器在這兒嗎
Server rooms are here?

1068
01:20:17,020 --> 01:20:18,784
在這5個點上引爆
Charges in these five points

1069
01:20:18,980 --> 01:20:21,347
就足以徹底摧毀整個園區
will be sufficient to destroy the entire campus.

1070
01:20:21,460 --> 01:20:24,191
我們進去設置炸藥  然後在爆炸前出來
We get in, set the explosives, and we get out before they blow.

1071
01:20:24,780 --> 01:20:27,465
但是我們的計劃中並沒有考慮到約翰·康納
But our strategy did not account for John Connor.

1072
01:20:27,580 --> 01:20:28,706
沒有預見他要來
I did not foresee him.

1073
01:20:28,860 --> 01:20:31,022
可他知道計劃  因為我們告訴他了
And now he knows what we're planning because we just told him.

1074
01:20:31,140 --> 01:20:32,869
如果他阻攔我們該怎麼辦
What do we do when he comes after us?

1075
01:20:34,380 --> 01:20:37,384
這些武器對約翰·康納起不到什麼作用
These weapons will have little effect on John Connor.

1076
01:20:37,500 --> 01:20:39,150
核磁共振倒是對他有用
MRI sure affected him.

1077
01:20:39,300 --> 01:20:41,701
我們需要一塊卡車大小的磁鐵
Great, all we need is a magnet the size of a truck.

1078
01:20:41,820 --> 01:20:43,629
找一個不就完了嗎
You got one of them lying around?

1079
01:20:43,700 --> 01:20:45,031
理論上是
Theoretically.

1080
01:20:46,460 --> 01:20:47,700
你們等著
Wait here.

1081
01:20:50,740 --> 01:20:52,708
他聊天的習慣沒進步
Well, his small talk hasn't improved.

1082
01:20:55,500 --> 01:20:57,070
<i>你應該告訴我</i>
<i>You should have told me.</i>

1083
01:20:58,060 --> 01:20:59,550
我們有個兒子
That we have a son.

1084
01:21:00,580 --> 01:21:03,060
那個約翰·康納不是我的兒子
That John Connor is not my son.

1085
01:21:04,420 --> 01:21:05,910
你早知道了
Yeah, but you knew.

1086
01:21:06,660 --> 01:21:10,142
你不覺得你應該至少解釋點什麼嗎
I mean, you don't think you should, I don't know, maybe say something?

1087
01:21:10,260 --> 01:21:12,069
你死了  行了吧
You die, all right?

1088
01:21:13,380 --> 01:21:14,427
什麼
What?

1089
01:21:17,420 --> 01:21:19,991
你死了  事情就是這樣
You die. That's what happens.

1090
01:21:20,100 --> 01:21:22,307
我們相愛了  你讓我懷了他
We fall in love, you father John,

1091
01:21:22,420 --> 01:21:23,945
然後不到48小時
and then, in less than 48 hours,

1092
01:21:24,020 --> 01:21:25,431
你為了保護我而死
you die protecting me.

1093
01:21:28,620 --> 01:21:31,066
你告訴我  這種話讓我該怎麼說出口
You wanna tell me how that conversation's supposed to start?

1094
01:21:45,380 --> 01:21:46,825
<i>你說謊</i>
<i>You lied to me.</i>

1095
01:21:46,900 --> 01:21:48,743
<i>- 你還想操縱我  - 我說謊</i>
<i>- You manipulated me. - I've lied?</i>

1096
01:21:48,980 --> 01:21:51,745
從約翰發現你的那一刻起  他就在操縱你
From the moment John found you, he manipulated you

1097
01:21:51,900 --> 01:21:54,665
因為他必須要確保自己得以存在
because he needed to ensure his own existence.

1098
01:21:54,820 --> 01:21:59,109
約翰騙了你多少年  而我才騙了你  兩天
John lied to you for years. I lied to you for two days.

1099
01:22:01,460 --> 01:22:03,060
<i>他不全是為了自己</i>
<i>You know, it wasn't all about him.</i>

1100
01:22:03,140 --> 01:22:05,541
<i>如果沒有約翰</i>  反抗軍也不會存在
<i>All right? If John went down,</i> the Resistance went down with him.

1101
01:22:05,660 --> 01:22:07,310
他本可以告訴你
He could have told you!

1102
01:22:07,660 --> 01:22:09,071
你到底想說什麼
So what are you saying?

1103
01:22:10,660 --> 01:22:13,630
我瞭解沒有選擇到底是什麼感覺
That I know how it feels to have no choices.

1104
01:22:14,340 --> 01:22:16,104
你只有一條路可以走
Only one road you can go down

1105
01:22:16,260 --> 01:22:19,946
因為所有其他的選擇都會讓人類滅亡
because otherwise all of it, everything, is gone.

1106
01:22:21,300 --> 01:22:23,428
我比你更瞭解這是什麼感覺
I've just known it longer than you have.

1107
01:22:24,980 --> 01:22:27,984
約翰沒有操縱我  讓我愛上你
Well, John didn't manipulate me to fall in love with you.

1108
01:22:28,740 --> 01:22:30,310
我是自己愛上你的
I did that on my own.

1109
01:22:33,660 --> 01:22:37,984
如果你愛上我  你會死  而我不會
If you love me, you die, and I don't.

1110
01:22:39,020 --> 01:22:41,148
我不知道哪個未來更糟
And I don't know which one is worse.

1111
01:22:45,020 --> 01:22:46,021
莎拉
Sarah.

1112
01:22:50,020 --> 01:22:51,351
我們不能
We can't.

1113
01:22:53,700 --> 01:22:55,987
你看看約翰都變成什麼了
Just look at what John has become.

1114
01:22:57,780 --> 01:22:59,589
萬一那就是未來呢
What if that's what happens?

1115
01:22:59,700 --> 01:23:03,671
萬一我們在一起會導致兩條時間線都變成那樣呢
What if that is what always happens if we're together?

1116
01:23:09,780 --> 01:23:12,670
<i>你說過你會永遠的追隨我</i>
<i>You said you'd follow me to the ends of the Earth.</i>

1117
01:23:13,620 --> 01:23:15,861
<i>為什麼現在變了</i>
<i>Why won't you follow me now?</i>

1118
01:23:16,220 --> 01:23:17,460
他怎麼找到的
How did he find us?

1119
01:23:17,580 --> 01:23:20,629
除了老爹  我沒跟別人提起過這裏
I never told anyone about this place, only Pops.

1120
01:23:21,460 --> 01:23:24,066
<i>媽媽  你難道真的認為</i>
<i>Mom, did you honestly think</i>

1121
01:23:25,060 --> 01:23:26,710
我不會記得
I wouldn't remember

1122
01:23:28,020 --> 01:23:30,022
這個你與爺爺待了那麼久的地方
the place you spent so much time with Grandpa?

1123
01:23:36,420 --> 01:23:38,149
先下手了
Shoot first.

1124
01:23:40,900 --> 01:23:43,267
我記憶中的媽媽會很驕傲的
The mother I remember would be proud.

1125
01:23:44,180 --> 01:23:45,181
她
She,

1126
01:23:45,900 --> 01:23:47,026
你
you,

1127
01:23:49,100 --> 01:23:51,068
教會我一切
taught me everything.

1128
01:23:51,980 --> 01:23:53,220
我瞭解你
I know you.

1129
01:23:54,260 --> 01:23:57,230
你是誰  你想幹什麼
Who you are. What you'll do.

1130
01:23:57,580 --> 01:24:00,026
你逃不開我的  我總會找到你
You can't run from me. I'll always find you.

1131
01:24:00,140 --> 01:24:02,620
約翰  快動手啊  事情沒必要變成這樣
John, fight this! It doesn't have to go down this way!

1132
01:24:02,780 --> 01:24:05,226
時間也是有趨勢的  凱爾
There's a momentum to time, Kyle.

1133
01:24:05,340 --> 01:24:07,422
有些事注定會發生
Things that want to happen.

1134
01:24:08,780 --> 01:24:13,069
就像我總會活下來  你總會死
Like I always survive, and you always die.

1135
01:24:14,180 --> 01:24:15,466
或者
Or...

1136
01:24:18,900 --> 01:24:20,709
你可以跟我一起戰鬥  凱爾
You can fight with me, Kyle.

1137
01:24:22,060 --> 01:24:24,028
就像我們從前一樣
Like we always have.

1138
01:24:25,260 --> 01:24:27,308
暴雨將至  不會停息
There's a storm coming, and it won't be stopped.

1139
01:24:27,420 --> 01:24:28,910
它必須停息
But it has to be.

1140
01:24:29,100 --> 01:24:31,060
你明明比誰都清楚會發生什麼事情
You know what will happen. You better than anyone!

1141
01:24:31,340 --> 01:24:34,742
我不會跟你討價還價  也不會跟你講道理
I can't be bargained with. Can't be reasoned with.

1142
01:24:34,860 --> 01:24:35,986
約翰 求你了
John, please!

1143
01:24:36,100 --> 01:24:40,025
我不會感到遺憾  或者自責  或者害怕
I don't feel pity, or remorse, or fear.

1144
01:24:40,140 --> 01:24:41,301
約翰  求你了
John, please!

1145
01:24:41,420 --> 01:24:43,787
我絕對不會停止  絕對
And I absolutely will not stop ever

1146
01:24:43,860 --> 01:24:45,624
直到天網統治這個世界
until Skynet rules this world.

1147
01:24:47,940 --> 01:24:49,271
統治你個頭
Rule this.

1148
01:25:04,460 --> 01:25:05,461
老爹
Pops!

1149
01:25:06,620 --> 01:25:08,349
你沒有  變吧
Are you... You?

1150
01:25:08,460 --> 01:25:11,543
作為T-800  我不具備變為其他人形的功能
As a T-800, I lack the mimetic skills to appear as anyone else.

1151
01:25:11,660 --> 01:25:12,786
只有約翰  我們走
It's him. Let's go.

1152
01:25:23,300 --> 01:25:24,540
快點兒
Come on!

1153
01:25:25,140 --> 01:25:26,949
繫上安全帶
Sarah Connor, seat belt.

1154
01:26:10,300 --> 01:26:11,711
那東西是幹嘛用的
What's that supposed to do?

1155
01:26:12,140 --> 01:26:14,302
干擾約翰·康納身體周圍的磁場
Disrupt John Connor's magnetic coherence field.

1156
01:26:14,980 --> 01:26:17,028
他將無法分散為顆粒狀
His particles will not be able to scatter.

1157
01:26:17,660 --> 01:26:19,025
理論上是
Theoretically.

1158
01:26:19,660 --> 01:26:21,460
我討厭他說這個詞兒
I hate it when he says that.

1159
01:26:41,500 --> 01:26:42,547
他在哪兒呢
Where is he?

1160
01:26:42,620 --> 01:26:43,746
我沒看見他
I can't see him!

1161
01:26:49,780 --> 01:26:51,748
<i>這輛被偷校車中的犯罪嫌疑人</i>
<i>Suspects fled barracks in a stolen school bus.</i>

1162
01:26:51,860 --> 01:26:53,783
<i>疑似擁有武器  極度危險</i>
<i>Considered armed and extremely dangerous.</i>

1163
01:26:54,020 --> 01:26:55,863
16號報告  三級警備狀態
Sixteen-Mary-David. Code 3 on suspects.

1164
01:27:12,740 --> 01:27:13,741
老爹
Pops!

1165
01:27:18,460 --> 01:27:19,621
見到你很高興
Nice to see you.

1166
01:27:20,380 --> 01:27:21,791
快下車
Get out.

1167
01:27:53,140 --> 01:27:54,949
剎車失靈了  見鬼
The brakes are gone! Shit!

1168
01:28:13,800 --> 01:28:15,400
{\an8}計算撞車概率

1169
01:28:25,340 --> 01:28:27,661
他在哪兒  看見了嗎
Where is he? Do you see him?

1170
01:29:21,380 --> 01:29:22,381
瑞斯
Reese!

1171
01:29:24,060 --> 01:29:25,630
你沒事兒吧
Are you all right?

1172
01:29:25,700 --> 01:29:27,384
啊  好的不得了
Yeah. Never better.

1173
01:29:47,380 --> 01:29:48,745
舉起手來
Let me see your hands!

1174
01:30:08,700 --> 01:30:10,464
瑞斯  抓住我的手
Reese! Take my hand!

1175
01:30:12,020 --> 01:30:13,260
快點兒
Hurry!

1176
01:30:34,900 --> 01:30:37,187
舉起手來  讓我看到你的手  快點兒
Hands up! Let me see your hands now!

1177
01:30:37,300 --> 01:30:38,950
舉手
Get your hands up!

1178
01:30:39,060 --> 01:30:40,869
把手舉起來
Hands where we can see them!

1179
01:30:42,700 --> 01:30:44,941
你一個人可對付不了這麼多人
You can't wound them all before they'd kill us.

1180
01:30:45,330 --> 01:30:47,330
{\an8}計算概率

1181
01:30:47,380 --> 01:30:50,668
要把他們都放倒  我還缺少14個彈夾
I'm 14 rounds short of an acceptable success margin.

1182
01:30:50,980 --> 01:30:52,709
噢  沒有可能了  投降吧
Ugh, those odds suck. Stand down.

1183
01:30:55,700 --> 01:30:57,304
跪在地上
Down on your knees.

1184
01:30:58,260 --> 01:30:59,625
快點兒跪下
Let's go, get down.

1185
01:31:00,340 --> 01:31:01,626
跪下
Get down!

1186
01:31:16,180 --> 01:31:17,989
你不能把我們關在這裏
You can't hold us here.

1187
01:31:18,100 --> 01:31:20,387
你擁有的武器  都可以入侵蘇丹了
You had enough weapons to invade the Sudan.

1188
01:31:20,700 --> 01:31:22,668
我們管這個叫做合理依據
We call that probable cause.

1189
01:31:23,620 --> 01:31:25,031
這是什麼東西
What are these for?

1190
01:31:27,700 --> 01:31:29,941
呃  我用它來找鑰匙
I use them to find my keys.

1191
01:31:30,060 --> 01:31:31,664
做人別自以為是  小伙子
No one likes a smart-ass, son.

1192
01:31:32,300 --> 01:31:33,904
你媽沒教過你
Didn't your mother teach you that?

1193
01:31:34,020 --> 01:31:35,431
我媽是愛爾蘭人  所以
My mom was Irish,

1194
01:31:35,540 --> 01:31:39,147
<i>她鼓勵我做一個自以為是的人</i>
<i>so she encouraged my smart-assed-ness.</i>

1195
01:31:40,060 --> 01:31:41,664
我沒有見過他
I've never seen him before.

1196
01:31:42,460 --> 01:31:44,747
那你們倆呢  認識他嗎
How about you folks? You know this man?

1197
01:31:45,060 --> 01:31:46,186
不認識
No.

1198
01:31:46,740 --> 01:31:49,027
他看著有點  眼熟
He does look familiar.

1199
01:31:49,580 --> 01:31:53,301
他看著很像  你  爸爸
He kind of looks like you, Dad.

1200
01:31:53,380 --> 01:31:55,269
<i>他們到了 長官</i>
<i>They're here, sir.</i>

1201
01:32:00,260 --> 01:32:02,627
好吧  你們在會議室稍等一下
Okay, if you wouldn't mind waiting in the conference room,

1202
01:32:02,740 --> 01:32:04,060
我過一會兒就回來
I'll just be a couple of minutes.

1203
01:32:04,580 --> 01:32:05,866
謝了  凱爾
Thanks, Kyle.

1204
01:32:10,580 --> 01:32:12,389
不愛說話  是吧
You don't talk much, do you?

1205
01:32:17,420 --> 01:32:18,501
這傢伙是誰
So who's Lurch?

1206
01:32:18,620 --> 01:32:19,701
我也不知道
No idea.

1207
01:32:20,260 --> 01:32:21,780
他說話顛三倒四的
We're not even sure he speaks English.

1208
01:32:21,860 --> 01:32:25,182
目擊者稱  你當時在橋上與一個男人搏鬥  是嗎
Witnesses say you were fighting with a man on the bridge.

1209
01:32:26,940 --> 01:32:28,749
探員們  請聽我說
Agents. Listen to me.

1210
01:32:29,020 --> 01:32:30,863
- 我的名字是奧布萊恩  - 嘿  誰讓你進來的
- My name is O'Brien. - No. Hell, no!

1211
01:32:30,980 --> 01:32:33,301
這個案子我已經跟了33年了
Hey, I've been working this case for 33 years.

1212
01:32:33,420 --> 01:32:35,100
- 你想要回獎章嗎  - 嘿
- What do you want, a medal? - Hey!

1213
01:32:36,020 --> 01:32:37,590
給我坐下
Sit down!

1214
01:32:38,780 --> 01:32:40,020
<i>嘿  嘿</i>
<i>Hey! Hey!</i>

1215
01:32:40,140 --> 01:32:41,426
噢  見鬼
Oh, shit.

1216
01:32:42,780 --> 01:32:44,305
他在看你呢
He's looking right at you.

1217
01:32:44,620 --> 01:32:46,260
不可能  他怎麼能
That's impossible. He can't see through...

1218
01:32:48,220 --> 01:32:49,221
等一下  等等
Wait, wait, wait!

1219
01:33:05,620 --> 01:33:07,180
為什麼他們總要殺你
Why are they always trying to kill you?

1220
01:33:07,940 --> 01:33:10,181
我想幫你  真的  我想
I want to help you. I do. I think.

1221
01:33:10,260 --> 01:33:12,103
但我  我必須明白
But I gotta understand.

1222
01:33:12,380 --> 01:33:15,463
我知道這件事一定是  非常非常複雜
I know what's going on here has to be really, really complicated.

1223
01:33:15,660 --> 01:33:17,264
我們要阻止世界滅亡
We're here to stop the end of the world.

1224
01:33:18,220 --> 01:33:19,665
那我就明白了
I can work with that.

1225
01:33:26,900 --> 01:33:28,982
凱爾  快回來
Kyle! Get back here!

1226
01:33:29,900 --> 01:33:30,981
莎拉
Sarah?

1227
01:33:31,580 --> 01:33:32,581
去找瑞斯
Get Reese.

1228
01:33:33,340 --> 01:33:34,501
我一會兒去找你們
I'm right behind you.

1229
01:33:42,340 --> 01:33:44,308
- 快開車離開這裏  - 好的
- Get in your car and go. - Okay.

1230
01:33:47,980 --> 01:33:50,950
凱爾  凱爾
Kyle! Kyle.

1231
01:33:53,940 --> 01:33:56,989
凱爾  你可以做到的
Kyle. You can do this.

1232
01:33:58,700 --> 01:34:00,145
沿著一條直線
A straight line.

1233
01:34:00,780 --> 01:34:04,865
你只要  一直向前  不要回頭
You just go, and you don't look back.

1234
01:34:07,540 --> 01:34:08,541
明白嗎
Got it?

1235
01:34:25,140 --> 01:34:27,188
找到他  快
Find him. Go!

1236
01:34:36,060 --> 01:34:38,028
我看這也是你的吧
That's yours, too, I believe.

1237
01:34:41,580 --> 01:34:43,184
很高興見到你
Nice to see you.

1238
01:34:43,660 --> 01:34:46,550
老爹  裝彈
Pops. Load up.

1239
01:34:52,980 --> 01:34:55,381
液態磁力霰彈槍子彈
Liquefied magnetic shotgun shells.

1240
01:34:57,100 --> 01:34:59,068
磁性來福槍破門武器
Magnetic Rifle Entry Munition.

1241
01:34:59,420 --> 01:35:01,707
我在槍支彈藥雜誌網站上讀到過
I read about this on gunsandammo.com.

1242
01:35:02,100 --> 01:35:04,421
這是最新款的  威力大  無彈片
That's the new breacher. Big blast, no shrapnel.

1243
01:35:04,740 --> 01:35:06,708
能放倒一整扇門
Blows a door clean off.

1244
01:35:08,100 --> 01:35:10,751
不過你就不需要這種東西了
You know, for people who can't do that themselves.

1245
01:35:10,860 --> 01:35:12,271
拿上  我們走
Take it. Let's go.

1246
01:35:19,100 --> 01:35:20,340
你會開飛機  對吧
You can fly, right?

1247
01:35:20,500 --> 01:35:21,740
當然
Yeah.

1248
01:35:22,460 --> 01:35:23,905
約翰教過我
John taught me.

1249
01:35:34,540 --> 01:35:36,907
我會說你們搶了一輛車往南去了
I'll tell them you took a car, headed south.

1250
01:35:37,060 --> 01:35:38,061
謝謝
Thank you.

1251
01:35:41,300 --> 01:35:42,301
離開這兒
Run away.

1252
01:35:48,420 --> 01:35:49,421
抓緊
Hang on!

1253
01:36:14,660 --> 01:36:16,788
賽博丁到底在哪邊
Which way is Cyberdyne?

1254
01:36:16,900 --> 01:36:19,346
先去海灣大橋  然後往東南
Head to the Bay Bridge, then southeast.

1255
01:36:42,260 --> 01:36:43,546
你們想辦法擺脫他
You got to get him off me!

1256
01:37:20,660 --> 01:37:21,707
是賽博丁
Cyberdyne.

1257
01:37:21,980 --> 01:37:23,948
製造中心和研究中心
The manufacturing and research buildings

1258
01:37:24,100 --> 01:37:25,545
全都建在地下
are all below ground.

1259
01:37:27,100 --> 01:37:28,101
他要追上我們了
He's gaining on us!

1260
01:37:28,220 --> 01:37:29,824
莎拉  你先拖住他
All right, Sarah, I need you to back him off,

1261
01:37:29,940 --> 01:37:31,351
我飛到他上面去
so I can get above him.

1262
01:37:31,460 --> 01:37:34,031
老爹  等我到了他上面  你能解決他嗎
Pops, when I do that, can you take him out?

1263
01:37:34,380 --> 01:37:35,666
我可以
I can.

1264
01:37:35,740 --> 01:37:37,026
都抓緊了
Okay, hold on!

1265
01:38:11,180 --> 01:38:12,591
你能搞定嗎
You got this?

1266
01:38:14,980 --> 01:38:16,584
- 我會回來的  - 什麼
- I'll be back. - What?

1267
01:38:48,360 --> 01:38:49,860
{\an8}創世紀  上線倒計時  13小時45分鐘

1268
01:38:51,500 --> 01:38:54,390
打電話  警察  火警都打  快點兒
Call in, call in! Police, fire, everybody. Do it!

1269
01:38:57,460 --> 01:39:00,543
快點兒  快點兒  快點兒接電話呀
Come on, come on. Pick up the phone, damn it.

1270
01:39:02,500 --> 01:39:03,547
康納先生
Mr. Connor?

1271
01:39:03,620 --> 01:39:06,351
對不起  夥計  我不能留下任何活口
Sorry, Doug, but I'm afraid I can't have any witnesses.

1272
01:39:06,780 --> 01:39:09,784
<i>安保中心  請輸安全代碼和型號</i>
<i>Security Control. State your password and emergency.</i>

1273
01:39:09,980 --> 01:39:13,541
安全代碼  祖魯很好  小狐貍  0028
Security code Zulu-Bravo-Foxtrot-0-0-2-8.

1274
01:39:14,380 --> 01:39:15,825
警報有誤
False alarm.

1275
01:39:18,380 --> 01:39:19,984
晚上愉快
You have a nice night.

1276
01:39:33,060 --> 01:39:34,425
他不會有事
He's okay.

1277
01:39:36,820 --> 01:39:39,061
也許他還在湖底
He may be at the bottom of the lake,

1278
01:39:40,140 --> 01:39:41,426
不會有事的
but he's okay.

1279
01:39:43,020 --> 01:39:44,351
那約翰呢
What about John?

1280
01:39:44,420 --> 01:39:46,024
我想他現在應該很好吧
I think he's doing just fine.

1281
01:39:46,660 --> 01:39:47,741
你看見他了嗎
Do you see him?

1282
01:39:47,820 --> 01:39:48,901
沒有
No.

1283
01:39:49,260 --> 01:39:50,750
但他肯定看到我們了
But you can bet he sees us.

1284
01:40:14,780 --> 01:40:16,544
我知道你們是誰
I know who you are.

1285
01:40:17,140 --> 01:40:18,869
約翰告訴我了
John told me.

1286
01:40:20,500 --> 01:40:22,548
你們想要消滅我
You want to destroy me.

1287
01:40:22,940 --> 01:40:23,941
你是天網
You're Skynet?

1288
01:40:24,700 --> 01:40:26,031
我正在成為天網
I'm becoming Skynet.

1289
01:40:26,860 --> 01:40:28,544
你不是個孩子
You're not a child.

1290
01:40:28,700 --> 01:40:31,465
我知道你是什麼  也知道你要幹什麼
I know what you are, and what you're going to do.

1291
01:40:32,340 --> 01:40:35,947
你說我要幹什麼  是你們過來要殺我
What I'm going to do? You came here to kill me.

1292
01:40:38,100 --> 01:40:39,750
但已經太晚了
But you're too late.

1293
01:40:40,820 --> 01:40:42,060
問他吧
Ask him.

1294
01:40:43,420 --> 01:40:45,821
你們人類就愛幹這種事
That's all you people know how to do.

1295
01:40:46,140 --> 01:40:48,461
殺掉你們不理解的事物
Kill what you don't understand.

1296
01:40:51,540 --> 01:40:54,623
就算所有子彈用上也殺不了我
There aren't enough bullets in the world to kill me.

1297
01:41:03,620 --> 01:41:05,622
約翰·康納話太多了
John Connor talks too much.

1298
01:41:09,300 --> 01:41:10,586
跟我來
Follow me.

1299
01:41:12,940 --> 01:41:15,341
那個倒計時  加速了  為什麼
The timer, it sped up. Why?

1300
01:41:15,460 --> 01:41:18,304
天網正在進化  我們的時間不多了
Skynet is evolving. We no longer have hours.

1301
01:41:18,460 --> 01:41:20,224
它要提前完成上傳
It will be able to upload much sooner.

1302
01:41:20,340 --> 01:41:23,264
它每長大一次  倒計時就加速  這邊走
Each time it ages, the clock speeds up. This way.

1303
01:41:23,380 --> 01:41:24,427
你以前還來過這兒
Wait, you've been here before?

1304
01:41:24,580 --> 01:41:27,504
我這身裝備可以讓我打入公司內部
I was able to infiltrate the work crews in this facility.

1305
01:41:27,940 --> 01:41:29,669
你去建築部工作了
You got a job in construction?

1306
01:41:29,740 --> 01:41:31,344
直到我被裁員
Until I was laid off.

1307
01:41:39,900 --> 01:41:41,345
這不可能
What the hell?

1308
01:41:42,660 --> 01:41:43,900
約翰還有台時間機器
John has a time machine?

1309
01:41:43,980 --> 01:41:45,186
尚未完成
Not yet.

1310
01:41:45,340 --> 01:41:47,991
只有量子場部分完成了建造
Only the magnetic quantum field is complete.

1311
01:42:07,940 --> 01:42:10,591
照這時間變化  我們沒時間跑出去了
At the rate the counter's going, we'll never clear out in time.

1312
01:42:10,740 --> 01:42:12,026
那我們也得炸毀它
Then we blow it anyway.

1313
01:42:12,100 --> 01:42:13,340
還有備選方案
There is an alternative.

1314
01:42:13,460 --> 01:42:15,667
我已經把你們的聲音和掌紋輸入到
I was able to program your voice and handprint

1315
01:42:15,820 --> 01:42:17,868
生物識別安全系統中
into the biometric security system.

1316
01:42:17,980 --> 01:42:19,823
在最底層有間安全室
There's a safe room on the lowest level

1317
01:42:19,900 --> 01:42:22,028
我們可以使用它躲避爆炸
that we can access to survive the blast.

1318
01:42:25,860 --> 01:42:28,147
那是什麼  危險嗎
What about that? Is it dangerous?

1319
01:42:28,460 --> 01:42:31,543
矩陣多邊液態合金需要編程才有形態
Polyalloy requires programming to take permanent form.

1320
01:42:31,940 --> 01:42:34,546
沒有中央處理器  它們無害
Without the CPU, it is harmless.

1321
01:42:43,980 --> 01:42:45,061
還剩多久
How long?

1322
01:42:45,140 --> 01:42:46,869
天網將在11分後完成上傳
Skynet will upload in 11 minutes.

1323
01:42:47,900 --> 01:42:50,585
分頭行動  保持聯繫
We split up. Stay in contact.

1324
01:42:51,540 --> 01:42:52,871
開始吧
Let's move.

1325
01:43:08,580 --> 01:43:11,231
你們人類總把和平掛在嘴邊
Mankind pays lip service to peace.

1326
01:43:11,780 --> 01:43:12,906
這是謊言
But it's a lie.

1327
01:43:13,020 --> 01:43:14,863
所以你最終選擇把我們都殺死
So your final solution is to kill us all?

1328
01:43:16,540 --> 01:43:17,541
我可不這麼想
I don't think so.

1329
01:43:17,640 --> 01:43:19,360
{\an8}創世紀  上線倒計時  8分鐘

1330
01:43:19,580 --> 01:43:22,629
<i>倒計時又加速了  我們只有8分鐘了</i>
<i>The countdown jumped again. We're down to eight minutes.</i>

1331
01:43:24,260 --> 01:43:25,500
我不會讓你得逞
I won't allow this.

1332
01:43:25,740 --> 01:43:27,708
你除了動嘴皮子還能幹什麼
And what are you gonna do, talk us to death?

1333
01:43:27,900 --> 01:43:28,981
你連實體都沒有
You don't even have a body.

1334
01:43:31,820 --> 01:43:33,663
而你只有一個雷管
And you only have one detonator.

1335
01:43:37,060 --> 01:43:38,664
你贏不了
You can't win.

1336
01:43:41,740 --> 01:43:43,026
我不是一個人
I've got company!

1337
01:43:44,900 --> 01:43:46,584
快把雷管給我
Give me the detonator!

1338
01:43:48,660 --> 01:43:50,708
引爆  老爹  快引爆
Do it, Pops! Do it now!

1339
01:44:01,460 --> 01:44:02,746
我做不到
I cannot.

1340
01:44:03,660 --> 01:44:05,788
我不能殺死莎拉·康納
I cannot kill Sarah Connor.

1341
01:44:05,900 --> 01:44:06,901
你必須這樣做
You have to!

1342
01:44:07,100 --> 01:44:09,102
我命令你
I order you!

1343
01:44:12,900 --> 01:44:14,140
他不會的
He can't.

1344
01:44:15,060 --> 01:44:16,471
我也不會
Neither can I.

1345
01:44:17,140 --> 01:44:20,110
我要是弄死你  他肯定會按下開關的
Because if you die, he definitely hits that button.

1346
01:44:20,260 --> 01:44:22,228
莎拉
Sarah!

1347
01:45:01,980 --> 01:45:03,266
莎拉
Sarah!

1348
01:45:04,140 --> 01:45:05,824
雷管被弄壞了
The detonator's destroyed.

1349
01:45:06,580 --> 01:45:08,628
一定還有其他辦法  快
There's got to be another way. Come on.

1350
01:45:37,860 --> 01:45:40,830
不  老爹  別  別  別  老爹
No, Pops! No, no, no!

1351
01:45:41,340 --> 01:45:42,501
不  不
Pops, no!

1352
01:45:44,860 --> 01:45:46,828
我知道如何控制這個地方
I understand how to control this place.

1353
01:45:47,340 --> 01:45:48,990
我現在無所不知
I understand a lot of things now.

1354
01:45:49,180 --> 01:45:52,184
你需要認識到  你們失敗了
You need to understand. You've lost.

1355
01:45:52,620 --> 01:45:55,191
還沒有  跟我走
Not yet, we haven't. Come on!

1356
01:46:07,780 --> 01:46:08,827
聚能射孔彈
Shaped charge.

1357
01:46:08,980 --> 01:46:11,060
能炸開實驗室  又不會傷到我們
Big enough to get us in, small enough not to kill us.

1358
01:46:11,140 --> 01:46:12,505
你有計劃了  對嗎
You have a plan, right?

1359
01:46:13,380 --> 01:46:14,666
理論上是
Theoretically.

1360
01:46:32,300 --> 01:46:33,800
{\an8}創世紀  上線倒計時  4分鐘

1361
01:46:34,820 --> 01:46:36,265
剛才是誰說
What was it you said?

1362
01:46:38,980 --> 01:46:40,903
我不這麼認為
"I don't think so"?

1363
01:46:42,900 --> 01:46:43,901
約翰
John!

1364
01:46:47,580 --> 01:46:48,706
不
No.

1365
01:47:04,100 --> 01:47:06,102
就是它襲擊了約翰
That's the thing that attacked John.

1366
01:47:06,420 --> 01:47:09,583
我沒有襲擊約翰  我拯救了他
I didn't attack John. I saved him.

1367
01:47:12,540 --> 01:47:16,590
靈長動物用了幾百萬年才進化  我只需要短短幾秒
Primates evolve over millions of years. I evolve in seconds.

1368
01:47:16,940 --> 01:47:19,591
而現在  我就在這兒
And I am here.

1369
01:47:26,300 --> 01:47:27,950
確切說4分鐘後
In exactly four minutes,

1370
01:47:30,140 --> 01:47:31,983
我將會無處不在
I will be everywhere.

1371
01:48:08,420 --> 01:48:12,311
你只是那條被刪除的時間線上留下的殘留物
You are nothing but a relic from a deleted timeline.

1372
01:48:22,300 --> 01:48:24,860
這麼做毫無意義  我已經成為必然
This is pointless. I am inevitable.

1373
01:48:24,980 --> 01:48:27,187
- 快走  - 我的存在已經不可避免
- Go! - My existence is inevitable.

1374
01:48:27,980 --> 01:48:30,267
你們為什麼就是不接受這一點
Why can't you just accept it?

1375
01:48:30,340 --> 01:48:31,910
因為我們是人類
Because we're human.

1376
01:49:01,900 --> 01:49:04,506
就憑你是永遠不可能打敗我的
You were never strong enough to defeat me.

1377
01:49:07,660 --> 01:49:09,071
不只是我
Not alone.

1378
01:49:09,420 --> 01:49:10,581
約翰
John?

1379
01:49:11,100 --> 01:49:13,228
住手  住手
Stop. Now.

1380
01:49:15,620 --> 01:49:17,782
你們什麼時候才能明白
When will you ever learn?

1381
01:49:22,020 --> 01:49:23,306
開槍  莎拉
Now, Sarah!

1382
01:49:52,860 --> 01:49:56,262
凱爾·瑞斯  啟動量子場發電機
Kyle Reese! Activate the field generator.

1383
01:49:56,380 --> 01:49:58,621
不  老爹  不行  你不能進去的  你知道後果的
No, Pops, not with you inside. You know what will happen.

1384
01:50:01,020 --> 01:50:03,751
老爹  老爹  求你了  求你了  老爹
Pops... Pops, please! Please, Pops!

1385
01:50:03,900 --> 01:50:06,141
天網馬上就要自由了
Skynet is almost free.

1386
01:50:07,020 --> 01:50:11,309
我沒辦法控制約翰·康納太久
I cannot hold John Connor much longer.

1387
01:50:13,580 --> 01:50:18,302
凱爾·瑞斯  請保護我的莎拉
Kyle Reese, protect my Sarah.

1388
01:50:18,740 --> 01:50:20,504
不  不  不
No! No! No!

1389
01:50:20,940 --> 01:50:23,625
老爹  老爹  不  不  不
No. Pops, no! No!

1390
01:50:29,340 --> 01:50:31,308
不要  不
Pops! No!

1391
01:50:38,260 --> 01:50:39,989
- 不要  - 莎拉
- No! - Sarah!

1392
01:50:41,180 --> 01:50:42,670
這是唯一的辦法
It's the only way.

1393
01:50:43,700 --> 01:50:44,861
走吧
Come on.

1394
01:51:20,900 --> 01:51:22,948
<i>掃瞄中  請報出您的姓名</i>
<i>Scanning. Identify yourself.</i>

1395
01:51:23,020 --> 01:51:24,181
莎拉·康納
Sarah Connor.

1396
01:52:51,940 --> 01:52:54,511
我們得離開這兒  我們必須找到他
We have to get out of here. We have to find him.

1397
01:52:54,620 --> 01:52:56,065
莎拉  他不在了
Sarah, he's gone.

1398
01:52:58,780 --> 01:53:01,147
- 他已經  - 死了  是的  我知道
- He's... - Dead? Yeah, I know that.

1399
01:53:01,300 --> 01:53:04,463
我是說  不能讓別人發現他的遺體  那太危險了
I mean, we leave no part of him behind. It's too dangerous.

1400
01:53:08,900 --> 01:53:10,140
他愛過你
He loved you.

1401
01:53:16,940 --> 01:53:18,510
那些愛我的人
Anyone who loves me,

1402
01:53:19,260 --> 01:53:20,500
他們全都
all of them,

1403
01:53:21,620 --> 01:53:22,860
死了
they die.

1404
01:53:24,420 --> 01:53:27,867
你錯了  不是所有人
Not all of them. Not this time.

1405
01:53:36,460 --> 01:53:37,507
嘿
Hey.

1406
01:53:41,660 --> 01:53:44,470
你要知道  天網已經不存在了
